Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,妳逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不過妳也不會懂 畢竟是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,站住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂奧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那些傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 被他們跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怪物吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,貝爾 貝爾
